{"tid":1281041,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"你地有冇試過去一間餐廳會咁呀？","createTime":"2019-07-03T07:17:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T15:58:35.000Z","uid":9934,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cc395edb6eb3fcaf3bb6b7eb52c5008046bcb28c","tid":1281041,"uid":9934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:17:17.000Z","msg":"去到坐底逼逼夾 又嘈 空氣又差<br />\n<br />\n廚房整啲野出黎又難食 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食客講話啲野難食 擺唔到落口喎<br />\n<br />\n全部夥計聽唔到睇唔到<br />\n<br />\n其他食客仲叫你地收聲 <br />\n<br />\n仲話我地食左咁多年咪又係咁食<br />\n<br />\n頂唔順拍下檯掟下野<br />\n<br />\n又要比班食開屎既食客話激進 <br />\n<br />\n講多兩句仲要比餐廳夥計打 <br />\n<br />\n仲要有人拍手叫好<br />\n<br />\n最係個間餐廳只有一間<br />\n<br />\n冇其他可以揀"},{"pid":"4e9a4f9401ef008497462d21db257cddcb4df8cd","tid":1281041,"uid":135798,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:21:01.000Z","msg":"邊間呀　開名"},{"pid":"ed9c6958de57a87931e74cfe715d2a1fae9cf551","tid":1281041,"uid":107571,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:22:05.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個老闆娘好柒<br />\n<br />\n兩個經理其中一個唔識英文<br />\n<br />\n成日有個老人痴呆阿伯同佢地企埋一齊"},{"pid":"3396f89b87b79524927c41b84ef91573446a1459","tid":1281041,"uid":18638,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4e9a4f9401ef008497462d21db257cddcb4df8cd","tid":1281041,"uid":135798,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:21:01.000Z","msg":"邊間呀　開名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:23:37.000Z","msg":"香港囉"},{"pid":"bef5b3c99425bfa8163d922baa04e035f077c433","tid":1281041,"uid":46076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:25:56.000Z","msg":"頂唔順拍下檯掟下野之前<br />\n已經有餐廳夥計拎住晒D棍出黎叫你走 同掟胡椒樽喇"},{"pid":"4c687d7571a8dd5c502206249a0493fbdbd3c6b3","tid":1281041,"uid":13467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:27:02.000Z","msg":"有班食開屎既人覺得自己係食家唔比人批評"},{"pid":"dd329a18d824150bdd87d31f93e78adcc8920678","tid":1281041